{
  "stem": "25834.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because so many times, so many thing happen to you, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're just-- Did you go down to where the areas that were burning were being destroyed?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this time, during the ghetto, one our-- not my friend, my brother friend, from the same class, was in a unit where has [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a plan and did destroy the wall and let the Jewish people go out and was not satisfy.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our friend-- not our, my brother friend, really, from the same class-- a nice boy, maybe 18, 20 years old, maximum-- was killed, 1 person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was maybe 30 people involved in this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one guy was shot by SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later, their-- the unit will not leave this guy in one piece and was very bad wounded.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Put the grenade and throw below him and was destroyed in the pieces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And wall in the-- hole in the wall was big enough, only people cannot go out, because action was not finished right.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wilk, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yuzek, if I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because all this is 50 years now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yuzek Wilk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wilk.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know the name, what was-- I mean this conspiracy name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yuzek Wilk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to-- and to also-- in a newspaper here, I saw this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first time I saw, in a high school, in Locust Valley High School, in newspaper was the memory of Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was this, and Wilk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, my goodness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I speech this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I give the lecture that I can say some [LAUGHS] nice word.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the-- was mentioned Wilk name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's-- that's fellow from AK, Armia Krajowa, mean Home Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was our obligation, if we can help Jewish people, do this.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
